content:
Skill:
15min of skill practice - pick your weakness:
Hand Stand (wall assisted/freestyle/walk)
Single/Double/Tripple Unders
Muscle-ups

Metcon:
Complete as many reps as possible in 8 minutes of:
Shoulder Press (#50/35)
Each time you break, perform 50 double-unders

Rest 4 minutes

Then, complete as many reps as possible in 8 minutes of:
Hang Power-Cleans (#70/50)
Each time you break, perform 30 air-squats
